body:
@raoyitao Our documentation is pretty comprehensive on this stuff:

http://docs.couchdb.org/en/latest/config/intro.html

@ceremcem THe error is indeed in what CouchDB is saying:

`{{badmatch,{error,eacces}}` is in your error output. That's a UNIX error, EACCESS, which means a permission problem.

This is also in our documentation:

https://docs.couchdb.org/en/latest/install/troubleshooting.html?highlight=eacces
